---
title: Breakfast Snack Board with Prosciutto plus Gouda, Apple, Pita Wedges & Creamy Apricot Spread
description: This one’s going out to all you grazers out there, the folks who like to eat with their fingers, creating perfect little bites of all sorts of treats. It’s our breakfast (or lunch or brunch!) snacking board, complete with warm fluffy pita triangles, luscious prosciutto, tart juicy apples, nutty gouda squares, crunchy almonds, and a sweet and creamy apricot spread for dipping and drizzling. It’s designed for your mixing and matching pleasure (and your no-pot-and-pan-washing pleasure, too!). Bon appetit!
